data.description: This 5 bedroom dwelling in Ennis is ready for your family to call home.  Situated on a culdesac and corner lot, the home provides ample space for any size family.  This home features oversized bedrooms, a great amount of storage space, large living areas and an updated kitchen.  Enjoy quality family time on the outdoor patio or gather around the fireplace in the spacious family room.  Home is currently financed with an assumable FHA loan with an interest rate of just over 3.7 percent.  Buyers who are interested in assuming the loan would need to qualify with Guild Mortgage.  Close to schools and businesses in the the endearing town of Ennis, the official Bluebonnet City and Trail of Texas.  Small town living in commuting distance to Dallas.  It doesn't get much better than this!  Information deemed reliable but buyers and buyers agent to verify all details herein.
